<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>후플레이 | Who Play?</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/match/room.css' />
    <script type="text/javascript"
        src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=4557e584626e7e40eb3f0835622a6f26"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/7.6.2/firebase-app.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/7.6.2/firebase-analytics.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/7.6.2/firebase-auth.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/7.6.2/firebase-database.js"></script>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/init.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/firebase_init.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/match/room.js"></script>
</head>
<div id="popOverlay" class="overlay">
    <div class="overlay-contents">
        <h1>Who Play?</h1>
        <h4>&</h4>
        <h3>Atech</h3>
        <p>Atech Soft에서 만든 'Who Play?'에서 발생 하는 모든 피해의 보상은 Atech Soft에서 책임지지 않습니다.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<body>
    <div id="leftSideMenu" class="sideMenu">
        <div class="side-content">
            <a href="/">Who Play?</a>
            <a href="/player/match">상대 매칭</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="main">
        <!--title bar-->
        <div class="input-table">
            <div class="input-table-header">
                <div class="table-header-cell room-title"><%=title%></div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-table-header">
                <div class="table-header-cell"><%=address%> - <%=detailAddr%></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="chat">
            <div id="chat-container">
            </div>
            <input type="text" maxlength="100" placeholder="메세지를 입력해주세요" id="send-msg">
            <button type="button" id="send-btn">전송</button>
        </div>

        <div class="user-map">
            <div id="kakaoMap"></div>
            <button id="calculate-btn">만날 지점 자동 계산</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>